wikipedia_page.main: Fiona Charlotte Denison (1970 – 9 January 2022) was a Scottish doctor and academic who was Professor and Honorary Consultant in Maternal and Fetal Medicine at the University of Edinburgh, founder of Birthing Solutions Ltd, and creator of the Birth Mirror.
